🛠️ Tier 3: Legacy & Transparency Audit Questions
To complete the framework, we move to Tier 3 (Legacy & Transparency). This tier focuses on ensuring the entity (AI, corporation, state) is accountable, transparent, and builds an ethical future, safeguarding against the very historical blind spots that cause the indignities you've cited.

